title: ADVANCED MIC.DEV. DL-,01 Revenue Breakdown – SWB:AMD – TradingView
text: ADVANCED MIC.DEV. DL-,01 revenue for the last year amounted to 20.55 B EUR, the most of which — 5.89 B EUR — came from its highest performing source at the moment, Data Center, the year earlier bringing 5.65 B EUR. The greatest contribution to the revenue figure was made by United States — last year it brought ADVANCED MIC.DEV. DL-,01 7.10 B EUR, and the year before that — 7.52 B EUR.
